---
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/base.css";
---

<Layout title="Mert Turkmenoglu">
    <header class="mx-4 sm:mx-0 mt-16">
        <img src="/profile.jpg" alt="Profile picture" width={128} height={128} class="rounded-full" />

        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-white font-bold mt-4">Mert Türkmenoğlu</h1>
        <ruby>/meɾt tyɾkmenoːɫu/</ruby>
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl">Software Engineer</h2>
        <hr class="border border-white w-11/12 sm:w-2/3 md:w-1/3 mt-2 px-4" />
    </header>

    <main class="mt-8 mx-4 sm:mx-0 text-base sm:text-xl">
        <div>
            Hi, my name is <abbr class="font-bold" title="/meɾt/">Mert</abbr>. I&apos;m a full-stack software engineer, a Kotlin enthusiast,
            and a violin player. I&apos;m interested in full-stack web development, programming languages, and design patterns.
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
            Currently, I&apos;m working on:
            <ul class="mt-2 ml-4 space-y-2">
                <li>
                    <a href="https://github.com/mertturkmenoglu/fringe" class="text-accent hover:underline hover:underline-offset-2">
                        Fringe
                    </a>, an operational intelligence and decision risk analysis tool.
                </li>

                <li>
                    <a href="https://github.com/mertturkmenoglu/wanderlust" class="text-accent hover:underline hover:underline-offset-2">
                        Wanderlust
                    </a>, a full-stack travel guide / location discovery application.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
            You can find me as <span class="text-accent">@mertturkmenoglu</span> or <span class="text-accent">@AsyncSquirrel</span> on most social
            media platforms.
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
            <Navigation />
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
